# Track only Jupyter notebooks and README files; ignore everything else
# 1) Ignore everything by default
*

# 2) Allow traversing into directories so unignored files can be found
!*/

# 3) Explicitly ignore notebook checkpoints and virtual documents (must be after !*/)
.ipynb_checkpoints/
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/**
.virtual_documents/
**/.virtual_documents/**

# 4) Allow project rules in .cursor/rules to be tracked
!**/.cursor/
!**/.cursor/rules/
!**/.cursor/rules/**

# 5) Always keep this ignore file itself
!.gitignore

# 6) Allow Jupyter notebooks
!**/*.ipynb

# 7) Allow README files (common case variants)
!**/README.md
!**/README.MD
!**/readme.md
